groupQpArray4[2]='<div id="quizpopper13"><div class="qpqvalue">Value: 10</div><div class="qpq"><form class="qp-form" name="f13"><fieldset><div class="qp-the-question"><legend><p>Camila is a Hispanic student who has just transferred to your class in the middle of a semester. While introducing herself, she says she is bilingual, but prefers Spanish rather than English. After few days, you realize that she seems discouraged because she is not grasping all content during class and may need some help.</p><p>Look at list below and select all methods (or tips) that you can use so Camila can learn better in your course.</p></legend></div><div class="qpindent"><div class="qp-m-answer-instruction">[mark all correct answers]</div><div class="qp-table"><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="a" id="q13a"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">a.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13a"><p>Refer her to the Writing Center to improve her English skills.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="b" id="q13b"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">b.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13b"><p>Develop proficiency in English by providing Camila with rich language experiences that integrate speaking, listening, reading, and writing.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="c" id="q13c"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">c.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13c"><p>Offer learning materials that are both in English and Spanish.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="d" id="q13d"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">d.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13d"><p>Develop individual projects where she can work on her own to catch up but still demonstrate the same skills and knowledge.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="e" id="q13e"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">e.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13e"><p>Tell her to use Google Translator so that she can become career ready on her own at her own pace.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="f" id="q13f"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">f.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13f"><p>Offer her videos that contain closed captioning to help her with understanding the content.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="g" id="q13g"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">g.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13g"><p>Ask her to turn in more work in writing than verbally so that she has time to form her thoughts.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="h" id="q13h"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">h.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13h"><p>Emphasize Camila&#39;s learning style strengths and match instructional resources and methods to her learning style preferences.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="i" id="q13i"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">i.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13i"><p>Decrease her anxiety by simply assigning her the grade she earned without much feedback and constructive criticism.</p></label></div></div><div class="qp-row"><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-left"><input type="checkbox" name="q13" value="j" id="q13j"></div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-middle">j.</div><div class="qp-m-answer-cell-right"><label for="q13j"><p>Provide examples, demonstrations, and optional resources that meet her needs.</p></label></div></div></div></div></fieldset></form><div class="collapse qpqfeedback" id="f_done13"></div><div class="collapse qpqfeedback2" id="feed13"></div></div></div>';
